Description: Provides functionality to calculate cost surfaces based on slope (e.g. Herzog, 2010; Llobera and Sluckin, 2007 <doi:10.1016/j.jtbi.2007.07.020>; Par√≠s Roche, 2002; Tobler, 1993), traversing slope (Bell and Lock, 2000), and landscape features (Llobera, 2000) to be used when modelling pathways and movement potential within a landscape (e.g. Llobera, 2015; Verhagen, 2013; White and Barber, 2012 <doi:10.1016/j.jas.2012.04.017>). 
